@TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@httpsAddress = https://localhost:5001

### 1. 取得所有停車場狀態（分頁）
GET {{TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress}}/api/parking-status?page=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. 取得特定停車場最新狀態
GET {{TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress}}/api/parking-status/P001
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. 取得特定停車場在特定時間的狀態
GET {{TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress}}/api/parking-status/P001/2025-11-05T10:30:00
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. 取得特定停車場的歷史記錄
GET {{TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress}}/api/parking-status/P001/history?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. 新增停車場狀態
POST {{TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress}}/api/parking-status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "P001",
  "updateTime": "2025-11-05T10:30:00",
  "availableCar": 50,
  "availableMotor": 20,
  "availableBus": 5,
  "availablePregnancy": 3,
  "availableHandicap": 2,
  "availableHeavyMotor": 1,
  "chargeTotal": 100,
  "chargeBusy": 30,
  "chargeIdle": 70,
  "reserved1": "預留欄位1"
}

###

### 6. 更新停車場狀態
PUT {{TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress}}/api/parking-status/P001/2025-11-05T10:30:00
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "availableCar": 45,
  "availableMotor": 18,
  "availableBus": 4
}

###

### 7. 刪除停車場狀態
DELETE {{TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress}}/api/parking-status/P001/2025-11-05T10:30:00

###

### 8. 取得所有不重複的停車場 ID
GET {{TaipeiSportsApi_HostAddress}}/api/parking-ids
Accept: application/json

###
